# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WorkPass AI — environment configuration
#
# The prototype runs 100% on MOCK services with NO env vars set. Every variable
# below is a "seam" toggle: set it to swap a mock implementation for a real one
# WITHOUT changing any frontend code. See ARCHITECTURE.md → "Migration path".
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# --- Verification engine -----------------------------------------------------
# Set this to enable the "Live AI" toggle in the dashboard. When present, the
# /api/verify route uses Claude to analyse a real uploaded document. When empty,
# the toggle is disabled and the app stays on deterministic mock results.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Model used by the Claude verification engine (optional override).
# WORKPASS_AI_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6

# --- Future production seams (NOT needed for the Vercel demo) -----------------
# Flip these on when you wire up real infrastructure. Each one maps to a single
# implementation swap in lib/config/container.ts.

# Postgres (Vercel Postgres / Neon) — swaps MockWorkerRepository for Drizzle.
# DATABASE_URL=

# Vercel Blob — swaps MockStorage for real document storage.
# BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=

# Background batch queue (Inngest / QStash) — swaps inline processing for a queue.
# QSTASH_TOKEN=

# Notifications (expiry reminders) — swaps MockNotifications for email/SMS.
# RESEND_API_KEY=
